OL,3,CAngry Ginge reveals mum's pets died in
OL,4,Chouse fire
OL,6,FStreamer and I'm A Celeb winner Angry
OL,7,FGinge has revealed him mum's pets died
OL,8,Fin a devastating house fire the day he
OL,9,Ftook part in Soccer Aid for UNICEF.
OL,11,FThe content creator from Eccles in
OL,12,FSalford ` whose real name is Morgan
OL,13,FBurtwistle ` shared an update to his
OL,14,Ffollowers on streaming platform
OL,15,FTwitch, confirming his mum's two cats
OL,16,Fand a rabbit died in the fire.
OL,18,FHe said he got a call on the morning
OL,19,Fof Soccer Aid, and his sister told
OL,20,Fhim: "Mum's house has blown up."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
