CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1780661502
OL,3,CAngry Ginge reveals mum's pets died in
OL,4,Chouse fire
OL,6,FThe 24-year-old told followers on a
OL,7,FTwitch stream that they are do not
OL,8,Fknow how the fire started, but he
OL,9,Fconfirmed no people were in the house
OL,10,Fas his mum was in London to watch him
OL,11,Fplay at the charity event.
OL,13,FHe said: "The story that we put on
OL,14,FInstagram of the living room, that was
OL,15,Fjust the tip of the iceberg. There is
OL,16,Fnot one thing in that house, and
OL,17,Fthat's why it's been so hard for my
OL,18,Fmum."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
