CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1780661502
OL,3,CAngry Ginge reveals mum's pets died in
OL,4,Chouse fire
OL,6,FGinge said the fire brigade believed
OL,7,Fthe fire had been smouldering in the
OL,8,Fhouse for "hours", and was contained
OL,9,Finside, until a neighbour attempted to
OL,10,Fgain entry at the side door to save
OL,11,Fthe pets in the house.
OL,13,FHe said: "As soon as the neighbours
OL,14,Fkicked the door in, the oxygen's met
OL,15,Fthe fire and the kitchen just
OL,16,Fexploded. Glass, everything, and
OL,17,Fthat's obviously took it to a new
OL,18,Flevel."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
