PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1780661502
OL,3,CAngry Ginge reveals mum's pets died in
OL,4,Chouse fire
OL,6,FHe said: "The hardest thing is just
OL,7,Fwatching my mum go through this. One
OL,8,Fnight, she had all of the belongings
OL,9,Fin her house and the next she has got
OL,10,Fnothing. She has literally just got
OL,11,Fthe suitcase she came to London with."
OL,13,FThe streamer told followers the house
OL,14,Fwas his grandad's, but he bought the
OL,15,Fhouse for his mum when they lost him
OL,16,Fto Covid.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
