PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1780661502
OL,3,CAngry Ginge reveals mum's pets died in
OL,4,Chouse fire
OL,6,FHe said: "I'll never sit here and say
OL,7,FI'm religious or anything like this,
OL,8,Fbut what I will say is, out of those
OL,9,Feight weeks, this is the only night
OL,10,Fshe didn't stay at the house.
OL,12,F"This is the only night she didn't
OL,13,Fstay at the house. And there's so many
OL,14,Fthings that happened. Soccer Aid's
OL,15,Fnever normally that week.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1780661502
OL,3,CAngry Ginge reveals mum's pets died in
OL,4,Chouse fire
OL,6,F"Soccer Aid could have easily been in
OL,7,FManchester, which meant she'd be in
OL,8,Fthe house. So, yeah, I just thank the
OL,9,FLord that my mum's okay. That's the
OL,10,Fbigger picture. Mum's okay, and that's
OL,11,Fwhat matters."
OL,13,FGinge also revealed he plans to
OL,14,Fdocument the process of rebuilding the
OL,15,Fhouse, saying: "I'm gonna make sure
OL,16,Fthat that is gonna be the best house,
OL,17,Fmy mum ever, ever has, or ever lives
OL,18,Fin."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
