OL,3,CAngry Ginge reveals mum's pets died in
OL,4,Chouse fire
OL,6,FEngland beat the World XI 3-2 in the
OL,7,FSoccer Aid match, with Ginge picking
OL,8,Fup player of the match for his
OL,9,Fperformance for England, playing the
OL,10,Ffull 90 minutes.
OL,12,FHe played alongside football stars and
OL,13,Fother celebrities including Wayne
OL,14,FRooney, Jill Scott, Tom Hiddleston and
OL,15,FOlly Murs.
OL,17,FAdolescence star Owen Cooper - who is
OL,18,Ffrom Warrington - made history as
OL,19,FSoccer Aid's youngest ever player, at
OL,20,Fjust 16.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
